\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Welcome to the final part of the Introduction: selecting your path,\u8221\'94 his Guide said with a broad smile. \u8220\'93As you have demonstrated exceptional abilities in multiple areas during the course of this introduction, you will be permitted to select both a class and a profession before the beginning of the tutorial. Additionally your options will be of higher quality and tailored to your performance in the introduction instead of being selected from the general starting list.\u8221\'94 She paused and allowed that to sink in. \u8220\'93Do you have any questions related to this process?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Uh\u8230\'85 not that I can think of, unless you can offer any advice on how to choose?\u8221\'94 Marcus answered, hoping he wouldn\u8217\'92t end up with so many good options he ended up paralyzed by indecision.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93The only advice I can offer is to chose the option that feels the most true to who you are and want to be,\u8221\'94 she answered. \u8220\'93Do you wish to choose class or profession first? Or do you need to a moment to consider?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Give me a moment,\u8221\'94 he replied automatically, \u8220\'93But do not let me waste more than ten minutes overthinking this.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Ten minutes begins now,\u8221\'94 she agreed with a nod.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marcus pulled up his status screen and begin looking it over, wanting to be sure he knew his strongest and weakest points before he started looking at his available paths. }
