\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 <$Scr_Ps::0>Skill: Dragon Scales (Ancient)}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Renowned for their strength, resilience and resistance to most magic, Dragon Scales are all the protection a true dragon really needs. You have chosen to follow in their footsteps, tapping into the very concept of Dragon Scales to turn your skin into a protective layer of Dragon Scales. For a small expenditure of mana, your skin turns into scales capable of deflecting physical blows and magic alike. While these are not yet the scales of a true dragon, they provide excellent protection and will continue to improve as your understanding of the concept deepens. Maintaining Dragon Scales slowly depletes your Soul Stability until they are dismissed as they are not yet fully part of you. May be dismissed at any time without cost. If damaged an additional small expenditure of mana will repair them. <!$Scr_Ps::0>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The ability to cover his skin in dragon scales to protect himself was going to be an incredible boon in combat. He activated the skill and watched as his skin was covered in scales that gleamed in colors ranging from a glossy chocolate brown to shiny metallic black. He moved around, bending and twisting, testing his flexibility and finding it completely unimpeded by the change. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Oh, I think I really like this,\u8221\'94 he muttered aloud. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93A Legendary class tied to the legacy of true dragons,\u8221\'94 the Guide sounded almost awed as it looked him over. [\u8220\'93That is\u8230\'85 beyond impressive.] However, time moves on swiftly and you have yet to select a profession.\u8221\'94[MARTY?]}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Oh\u8230\'85 yeah. Sorry, got kinda caught up in how badass this class is and forgot,\u8221\'94 Marcus admitted sheepishly before dismissing the scales. The vanished instantly, but he noticed that his patches of natural scales had spread somewhat and now reflected the same glossier colorations as his conjured scales. Interesting.}
